	(1, 'Company overview', 'company-overview', '<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1543300630305"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_custom_1543300691469 text_align_left"><h2 style="text-align: left;font-family:Poppins;font-weight:700;font-style:normal">Company overview</h2></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1693815556049">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<p><img decoding="async" class="alignleft wp-image-2609 size-full" src="http://staging.shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/company-overview.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="257" srcset="https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/company-overview.jpg 450w, https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/company-overview-300x171.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px">PT Shinta Inserve is a specialist in insurance brokerage and consulting services. We have been serving clients across a variety of industries since our inception in 1990, and have obtained a license from the Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia, which was ratified by Decree No.KEP.167/KM.13/1990.</p>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="wpb_raw_code wpb_content_element wpb_raw_html">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<div style="clear: both;"></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1692004492968">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<blockquote><p>\r\n<strong>Our vision is to be a trusted leading insurance brokerage company, dedicated to providing the best insurance consultancy and solutions to appropriately protect our clients’ assets and financial future.</strong>\r\n</p></blockquote>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class="vc_custom_heading no_stripe vc_custom_1692005285532 text_align_left"><h4 style="color: #222222;text-align: left;font-weight:700">Our Mission</h4></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<ul>\r\n<li><strong><em>To act professionally on behalf of our clients, to provide the best insurance solutions and services that have been tailored to their individual requirements and needs.</em></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><em>To be a professional company that is dedicated to client statisfaction by producing the best-quality results with excellent service.</em></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><em>To establish a warm, cooperative relationship with clients and partners on the way to creating a healthy, friendly business climate.</em></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><em>To manage our company effectively efficiently and competitively, and position it to contribute robustly to our industry</em></strong><strong>.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_custom_heading no_stripe vc_custom_1531204916739 text_align_left"><h4 style="color: #222222;text-align: left">Our commitment</h4></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<ul>\r\n<li>Our clients are our most precious partners. We take responsibility to truly understand our client’s core business and values and building a lasting relationship with our clients.</li>\r\n<li>Our top concern is to provide our clients with 100% satisfactory service.</li>\r\n<li>We capitalize on our good reputation and solid relations with leading insurers in the market, and to provide our clients with the widest insurance coverage at the most competitive premium price.</li>\r\n<li>We deliver innovative insurance solutions through qualified professionals, who have a wide range of experience and expertise in insurance and risk management.</li>\r\n<li>Backed with outstanding claim negotiation skills and deep institutional knowledge, we provide clients with the best claim and settlement solutions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_custom_heading no_stripe vc_custom_1453471549250 text_align_left"><h4 style="color: #222222;text-align: left">How we work</h4></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Gathering data and information</strong> – Armed with statistical knowledge and technical expertise, we make fact-based prediction and analysis to anticipate and address the risk that your business may face.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Risk assessment and management</strong> – We focus on creating the right strategy to assess, design, and implement the optimum framework to ensure our client’s risk is appropriately managed.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Risk profiling and customized insurance protection</strong> – Based on concrete data and information, we assess and tailor the most effective framework that supports and protects your business.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Communicating and negotiating with insurance companies</strong> – Our financial experts help you analyze financial data and create a rock steady financial foundation that helps you to leverage and strengthen your position.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Presenting the insurance program to the client</strong> – Our multidiscipline team of professionals works along side with you to assess the most specific and cost-effective insurance program that caters to your company’s needs and requirements.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Issuing insurance documentation to secure the risk</strong> – We are dedicated to meet our words with coordination and competence to help you realize your vision.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Claims handling and insurance consultancy during the insurance period</strong> – You can always count on us to provide professional consultation and personalized service. In times of crisis, we are ready to take over responsibility to accelerate claim process so your business can continue to run as usual.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', NULL, 1, 0, 'asdfas', 'asdf', 'asdf', 'dsf', '2025-04-18 09:52:22'),
	(2, 'Company history', 'company-history', '<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1543301402781"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_custom_1543301373200 text_align_left"><h2 style="text-align: left">Company history</h2></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1693816605882">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<p><img decoding="async" class="alignleft wp-image-2620 size-full" src="http://staging.shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/shinta-inserve-office.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="338" srcset="https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/shinta-inserve-office.jpg 450w, https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/shinta-inserve-office-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px">PT Shinta Inserve is a specialist in insurance brokerage and consulting services. We have been serving clients across a variety of industries since our inception in 1990, and have obtained a license from the Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia, which was ratified by Decree No.KEP.167/KM.13/1990.</p>\r\n<p>Every client occupies a special place at PT Shinta Inserve. We recognize that each has a unique combination of needs and requirements. From the start of every partnership, we are committed to delivering a distinctive suite of services built specially with those demands in mind. From there, we work tirelessly to ensure that every client’s business is protected adequately and on all fronts, to their satisfaction. We help manage risk, and assist in planning long-term strategies, to provide the fullest insurance coverage.</p>\r\n<p>To achieve this, we choose to work with the best team of experts across Indonesia. Each member has extensive expertise and substantial networks in a chosen field and through this steadfast support, we are well-equipped to consistently provide the best service to each client.</p>\r\n<p>Your trust is our priority. We are resolute in our pursuit of service excellence, and work every day to refine our knowledge and expertise, as well as build on our decades of experience, to be able to continue providing quality financial advisory services to all partners and clients.</p>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="company_history">\r\n			<ul>\r\n			<li>\r\n	<div class="year">Nov 1989 </div>\r\n	<div class="sep"></div>\r\n	<div class="company_history_text">\r\n		<h4 class="no_stripe"></h4>\r\n		<p>The establishment of PT. Shinta Insurance Brokers was legalized by notary Buniarti Tiandra<br>\r\nS.H.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</li><li>\r\n	<div class="year">Dec 1989</div>\r\n	<div class="sep"></div>\r\n	<div class="company_history_text">\r\n		<h4 class="no_stripe"></h4>\r\n		<p>Officially obtained a Business License from the Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia based on Decree No. KEP.167/KM.13/1990.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</li><li>\r\n	<div class="year">Aug 1990</div>\r\n	<div class="sep"></div>\r\n	<div class="company_history_text">\r\n		<h4 class="no_stripe"></h4>\r\n		<p>Formally registered as a member of Asosiasi Perusahaan Pialang Asuransi dan Reasuransi Indonesia (APPARINDO) with Decree Number No. 033-1990/APPARINDO.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</li>		</ul>\r\n	</div></div></div></div>', NULL, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-23 09:09:28'),
	(3, 'What is insurance brokers ?', 'what-is-insurance-brokers', '<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1543388704526"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_custom_1692001465368 text_align_left"><h2 style="font-size: 25px;text-align: left;font-family:Poppins;font-weight:600;font-style:normal">What is insurance brokers ?</h2></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1693815715161">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<p><img decoding="async" class="alignleft wp-image-2613 size-full" src="http://staging.shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-insurance.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="300" srcset="https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-insurance.jpg 450w, https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-insurance-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px">Insurance brokers work as facilitators between clients and insurance companies. We provide initial services for clients who want to purchase insurance to gain protection for their assets that suits their needs. Compiling a list of various types and costs of insurance is just the first step in each partnership. You will also get complete and detailed information pertaining to each recomendation we make. As a professional firm with broad expertise for various types of insurance policies, our services will make it easy for you to find efficient and comprehensive insurance at the best price.</p>\r\n<p><strong>HOW WE WORK</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Through interviews and surveys, wecollect data and information regarding your specific needs.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>After assessing the risks involved, we identify areas requiring risk management.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>We finetune your individual risk profile and design a bespoke insurance protection plan.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>We negotiate with insurance companies on your behalf.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>After securing the agreement of all parties involved, we present you with a complete insurance program.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>We issue the relevant insurance documentation to mitigate your risk.</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>For as long as your insurance is valid, we provide comprehensive consultation and claim services.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div></div></div>', NULL, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-23 09:35:40'),
	(4, 'Our approach', 'our-approach', '<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1543301560021"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_custom_1543301546617 text_align_left"><h2 style="text-align: left">Our approach</h2></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1693815618190">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<p><img decoding="async" class="alignleft wp-image-2611 size-full" src="http://staging.shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/our-approach.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="297" srcset="https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/our-approach.jpg 450w, https://shintainserve.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/our-approach-300x198.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px">We believe that a consulting firm should act more than an advisor, therefore we approach every client’s business as if it were our own. To truly understand the core of our client’s business, we put ourselves in our client’s shoes and align our incentives with their objectives. Through a deep and personalized collaboration, we help our clients to unlock the full potential of their business and realize their vision.</p>\r\n<p>The right approach is necessary for the right outcome. We approach our work by applying technical insight to our client’s internal way of doing work. We know that in order to maximize the potential of success for your company, we need to shape our expert advice in a way that applies to your way of doing business. This allows us to foster a rich relationship that is mutually beneficial for everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1543302191612"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n\r\n	                    <div class="icon_box hexagon hexanog_animation style_1 icon_left clearfix">\r\n                                    <div class="icon font-color_default font-color_base_bg" style="width:75px"><i style="font-size:25px;  " class="fa fa-info"></i></div>\r\n                        <div class="icon_text">\r\n                                    <h5 class="font-color_base no_stripe">Gathering data and information</h5>\r\n                                <p>Armed with statistical knowledge and technical expertise, we make fact-based prediction and analysis to anticipate and address the risk that your business may face.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        	\r\n\r\n\r\n	                    <div class="icon_box hexagon hexanog_animation style_1 icon_left clearfix">\r\n                                    <div class="icon font-color_default font-color_base_bg" style="width:75px"><i style="font-size:21px;  " class="stm-binoculars"></i></div>\r\n                        <div class="icon_text">\r\n                                    <h5 class="font-color_base no_stripe">Risk profiling and customized insurance protection</h5>\r\n                                <p>Based on concrete data and information, we assess and tailor the most effective framework that supports and protects your business.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        	\r\n\r\n\r\n	                    <div class="icon_box hexagon hexanog_animation style_1 icon_left clearfix">\r\n                                    <div class="icon font-color_default font-color_base_bg" style="width:75px"><i style="font-size:27px;  " class="stm-amsterdam-presentation"></i></div>\r\n                        <div class="icon_text">\r\n                                    <h5 class="font-color_base no_stripe">Presenting the insurance program to the client</h5>\r\n                                <p>Our multidiscipline team of professionals works along side with you to assess the most specific and cost-effective insurance program that caters to your company’s needs and requirements.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        	\r\n\r\n\r\n	                    <div class="icon_box hexagon hexanog_animation style_1 icon_left clearfix">\r\n                                    <div class="icon font-color_default font-color_base_bg" style="width:75px"><i style="font-size:27px;  " class="stm-ppl_outline"></i></div>\r\n                        <div class="icon_text">\r\n                                    <h5 class="font-color_base no_stripe">Claims handling and insurance consultancy during the insurance period</h5>\r\n                                <p>You can always count on us to provide professional consultation and personalized service. In times of crisis, we are ready to take over responsibility to accelerate claim process so your business can continue to run as usual.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        	\r\n</div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n\r\n	                    <div class="icon_box hexagon hexanog_animation style_1 icon_left clearfix">\r\n                                    <div class="icon font-color_default font-color_base_bg" style="width:75px"><i style="font-size:22px;  " class="stm-graph"></i></div>\r\n                        <div class="icon_text">\r\n                                    <h5 class="font-color_base no_stripe">Risk assessment and management</h5>\r\n                                <p>We focus on creating the right strategy to assess, design, and implement the optimum framework to ensure our client’s risk is appropriately managed.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        	\r\n\r\n\r\n	                    <div class="icon_box hexagon hexanog_animation style_1 icon_left clearfix">\r\n                                    <div class="icon font-color_default font-color_base_bg" style="width:75px"><i style="font-size:23px;  " class="stm-mans"></i></div>\r\n                        <div class="icon_text">\r\n                                    <h5 class="font-color_base no_stripe">Communicating and<br>\r\nnegotiating with insurance companies</h5>\r\n                                <p>Our financial experts help you analyze financial data and create a rock steady financial foundation that helps you to leverage and strengthen your position.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        	\r\n\r\n\r\n	                    <div class="icon_box hexagon hexanog_animation style_1 icon_left clearfix">\r\n                                    <div class="icon font-color_default font-color_base_bg" style="width:75px"><i style="font-size:19px;  " class="fa fa-book"></i></div>\r\n                        <div class="icon_text">\r\n                                    <h5 class="font-color_base no_stripe">Issuing insurance documentation to secure the risk</h5>\r\n                                <p>We are dedicated to meet our words with coordination and competence to help you realize your vision.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        	\r\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', NULL, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-26 08:39:54'),
	(5, 'Benefits For You', 'benefits-for-you', '<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1543301665575"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_custom_heading vc_custom_1543301646955 text_align_left"><h2 style="text-align: left">Benefits for you</h2></div>\r\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1691382131820">\r\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n			<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Savings on Insurance Costs</strong><br>\r\nOur wide network of reputable insurance companies ensures that our client have the best options available in the market.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Professional Claim Handling and Settlements</strong><br>\r\nOur deep technical expertise and industry insight prepares us to negotiate and accelerate process of claim and settlement to our client’s best interest.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Risk Management</strong><br>\r\nWe focus on creating the right strategy to assess, design, and implement the optimum framework to ensure our client’s risk is appropriately managed.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Objective and Professional Advice</strong><br>\r\nQualified and fully-licensed professional to advise our client with clear and transparent guidance on the most competitive premium rates that protect every aspects of our client’s business.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Better Terms and Conditions</strong><br>\r\nWe leverage our unique market strength to provide the most cost effective insurance terms available to our clients.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Greater Bargaining Power</strong><br>\r\nProvides innovative strategy and unparalleled market knowledge to strengthen our client’s bargaining position.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Low Administrative Duties</strong><br>\r\nCompetent and professional staffs who handles your legal documentation and other administrative duties from issue to claim.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h5><strong>Our Commitment</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Our clients are our most precious partners. We take responsibility to truly understand our client’s core business and values and building a lasting relationship with our clients.</li>\r\n<li>Our top concern is to provide our clients with 100% satisfactory service.</li>\r\n<li>We capitalize on our good reputation and solid relations with leading insurers in the market, and to provide our clients with the widest insurance coverage at the most competitive premium price.</li>\r\n<li>We deliver innovative insurance solutions through qualified professionals, who have a wide range of experience and expertise in insurance and risk management.</li>\r\n<li>Backed with outstanding claim negotiation skills and deep institutional knowledge, we provide clients with the best claim and settlement solutions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div></div></div>', NULL, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-26 08:49:35'),
